# Missions Admin Portal Extension

Extend the existing admin portal to manage all Missions content (Campaigns, Summits, Conferences) — both listing pages and individual event detail pages — following the same localStorage + fallback pattern used for Home / About / Impact.

## Proposed Changes

### Data Layer

#### [MODIFY] [adminData.ts](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/lib/adminData.ts)

Add new types and CRUD helpers for Missions data. New localStorage keys:

| Key | Section | Type |
|-----|---------|------|
| `campaigns_impact_stats` | Campaign Impact Metrics (4 records) | `{ stat_number, stat_label }[]` |
| `campaigns_past` | Past Campaigns list | `{ campaign_id, campaign_title, campaign_date, campaign_image }[]` |
| `campaigns_upcoming` | Upcoming Campaign (0-1) | `{ is_active, campaign_name, description, date_time, location, register_url, promo_image }` |
| `campaigns_details_{id}` | Individual campaign details | Full campaign object (hero, about, impact, partners, gallery) |
| `summits_hero_gallery` | Summit Hero (3 images) | `string[]` |
| `summits_impact_stats` | Summit Impact Metrics (4 records) | `{ stat_number, stat_label }[]` |
| `summits_past` | Past Summits list | `{ summit_id, summit_title, summit_date, summit_image }[]` |
| `summits_upcoming` | Upcoming Summit (0-1) | `{ is_active, summit_name, description, date_time, location, register_url }` |
| `summits_details_{id}` | Individual summit details | Full summit object (hero, about, impact, speakers, partners, gallery) |
| `conferences_hero_gallery` | Conference Hero (2 images) | `{ primary_hero_image, secondary_hero_image }` |
| `conferences_impact_stats` | Conference Impact Metrics (4 records) | `{ stat_number, stat_label }[]` |
| `conferences_past` | Past Conferences list | `{ conference_id, conference_title, conference_date, conference_image }[]` |
| `conferences_upcoming` | Upcoming Conference (0-1) | `{ is_active, conference_name, description, date_time, location, register_url, promo_image }` |
| `conferences_details_{id}` | Individual conference details | Full conference object (hero, about, impact, news, speakers, partners, gallery) |

