### Admin Routes

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/app/admin/layout.tsx)

Add "Missions" section to sidebar nav with sub-items: Campaigns, Summits, Conferences (expandable group).

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/app/admin/page.tsx)

Add Missions cards (Campaigns, Summits, Conferences) to the dashboard grid.

#### [NEW] [campaigns/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/app/admin/missions/campaigns/page.tsx)

Tabbed admin form with 4 tabs:
1. **Impact Stats** — 4 editable records (`stat_number` + `stat_label`)
2. **Past Campaigns** — add/edit/delete campaign list items (title, date, image URL)
3. **Upcoming Campaign** — toggle `is_active`, edit campaign_name, description, date_time, location, register_url, promo_image
4. **Campaign Details** — select a campaign from past list → edit full individual detail (hero video, about text, action items, impact metrics, partners, gallery)

#### [NEW] [summits/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/app/admin/missions/summits/page.tsx)

Tabbed admin form with 5 tabs:
1. **Hero Gallery** — manage 3 highlight images
2. **Impact Stats** — 4 editable records
3. **Past Summits** — add/edit/delete summit list items
4. **Upcoming Summit** — toggle + fields (same schema as upcoming campaign)
5. **Summit Details** — select a summit → edit full individual detail (hero, about, impact, speakers, partners, gallery)

#### [NEW] [conferences/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Owolabi%20Agbabiaka/Desktop/Website/app/admin/missions/conferences/page.tsx)

Tabbed admin form with 5 tabs:
1. **Hero Images** — 2 hero images (primary + secondary)
2. **Impact Stats** — 4 editable records
3. **Past Conferences** — add/edit/delete conference list items
4. **Upcoming Conference** — toggle + fields
5. **Conference Details** — select a conference → edit full individual detail (hero, about, impact, news cards, speakers, partners, gallery)

